cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the use of algorithms to mimic the divergent evolutionary process in nature to find high-performing solutions. This topic is closely related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also introduces a new variation operator to accelerate the algorithm, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the effectiveness of the algorithm in solving three different problems, which is a common theme in the field of neural networks (cs.NE).
